title.narrative: Comprehensive Child Care Program (PAININ, Phase IV)
Programa de Atencion Integral a la Niñez (PAININ Etapa IV)

description.narrative: El objeivo del programa es apoyar el desarrollo sico social, cognitivo y fisico de los ninios de las comunidades mäs marginadas para asegurar su ingreso oportuno al primer grado.
The aim of the Program is to support the psychosocial, cognitive and physical development of low-income children under six years of age to ensure their timely entry the formal education system.
